Pobblebonk FAQ

What is Pobblebonk? Pobblebonk is the app to help people discover and support the live stand up comedy scene socially.
Do I have to create an account to use it? No, it is a free app that you can enjoy without an account.
How are you helping people discover and support the live stand up scene? When you log in as a fan you can see who is getting favorited by other fans lately around you. When you go and check into a show, you can "favorite" your top two comics that night. You can follow your friends and see who they've seen and voted for lately. When you travel to a different city you'll be able to help determine that city's top comic. Fan interaction either through votes given or letting the app know that you saw a comic are recorded and have the most effect on the End Of Year Awards. You can also list what comedian you want to see come to your city. In the future, if there are a lot of people that want to see a comedian, we can let that comedian know! When comedians interact with the app, they are getting their name out there to the most hardcore stand up comedy fans. They may even get a tip from the audience because the app makes their venmo/cash app visible.
